For starters, you can be cheesy by telling one of those jokes that involve a knock at the door and results in a huge eye roll when the answer is nothing but a lame pun. But how can you get to the good kind of cheesy? Like cheesy cheesy. Simple, take the Cheesy Bean and Rice Burrito for example. With a perfect combination of warm nacho cheese sauce, refried beans and premium seasoned rice all wrapped in a soft flour tortilla, its the kind of cheesy you definitely wantand nobody has to answer whos there to get it.
product.webDescriptionSubtitleText: How To Get Cheesy Without Being Cheesy. The Cheesy Bean and Rice Burrito has a few tips for you.
product.webProductDescription: So theres cheesy, and then theres cheesy. How do you differentiate the two? Because both clearly have two totally different meanings. For starters, you can be cheesy by telling one of those jokes that involve a knock at the door and results in a huge eye roll when the answer is nothing but a lame pun. Dont get it twisted. We got nothing against puns. Were just looking out for you so you can avoid the cheesy ones. If you have a good pun, pun away. Pun away, friend. But how can you get to the good kind of cheesy? Like CHEESY cheesy. Simple. Take the Cheesy Bean and Rice Burrito for example. With a perfect combination of warm nacho cheese sauce, refried beans, creamy jalapeo sauce and seasoned rice all wrapped in a soft flour tortilla, its the kind of cheesy you definitely wantand nobody has to answer whos there to get it. The only thing theyll want answered is how to get their hands on more. And you know what, we have answers for that question. See, were full of knowledge here at Taco Bell. You really dont have to do much to get yourself a Cheesy Bean and Rice Burrito. For starters, you can just make your way to a restaurant and order that cheesy enchantment. Or you can order it right here and right now. But since youre right here reading this description, you probably already know that. If youre like, Whoa! No way! Our answer is, Yeah, way. So get your order on and get yourself a Cheesy Bean and Rice Burrito. You wont regret it. And remember, the Cheesy Bean and Rice Burrito is anything but the lame type of cheesy, but its all the good type of cheesy.
